                    "company": "Wageningen University & Research",
                    "description": "Short term assignment to write up the work we did on integrated co-learning on mineral fertiliser-use in East-African highland banana farming systems in Uganda. The work describes how co-learning farmers changed their perception on mineral fertiliser-use due to the co-learning activities and actively started using mineral fertilisers in their plantations. Moreover, we describe how banana yields were assessed in smallholder systems and what determined these yields.",
                    "title": "Postdoctoral Researcher at the Plant Production Systems group",
                    "employment_type": null
                },
                {
                    "location": null,
                    "date": {
                        "start": {
                            "month": 8,
                            "day": null,
                            "year": 2016
