                    },
                    "company": "Wageningen University & Research",
                    "description": "The objective of this thesis research was to sustainably intensify maize cropping systems through the use of cowpea-maize relay cropping. An experiment was conducted in smallholder farmer fields in two agro-ecological zones of northern Ghana and farmers were interviewed on their current cowpea cultivation practices. This research was part of the N2Africa project of the Plant Production Systems group of Wageningen University.",
